commitResults.messageTitle: Move all logic in LogicManager to model
commitResults.messageBody: The reason behind this is that Logic should only act as a compatibility layer. By moving all the logic to Model, future new functions can use those methods in a downward fashion (all logic calls go to Model) instead of calling upwards (low level classes call high-level Logic interface). Also, it will make Logic to have a single responsibility only: act as a compatibility layer between the front-end and the back-end
